Constructor Detail

DLLNode

public DLLNode(DLLNode previous,
               DLLNode next,
               java.lang.Object o)
Constructor creates a Node that has references to a next node and a previous node. To create a head node, make the previous parameter a null. To create a tail node, make the next parameter a null.

Parameters:
previous - - DLLNode that refers to the previous item in the list
next - - DLLNode that refers to the next item in the list
o - - Object that is stored in the node.
